questionsAndAnswers.question: What do you need to get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: We require you to provide a domain & hosting. If you haven't purchased these yet, feel free to reach out, and we'll recommend reliable and affordable options. Additionally, we'll need your website logo, content for all pages (text + images), and a reference website if you'd like to show any.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will my website be mobile-friendly?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, absolutely! All websites are designed to be mobile-friendly, which means they will look great and function properly on any device, including Desktop, Smartphones and Tablets.

questionsAndAnswers.question: I do not have the content, can we start?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Of course! We'll use placeholder content like "Lorem Ipsum," which is completely generic and plagiarism-free, allowing you to easily replace it with your own industry-specific content later on.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will I be able to manage the website and update the content later on?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, absolutely! We design the website to be user-friendly, so you'll be able to manage it and edit content with ease. If needed, we can also provide guidance or a tutorial to help you get started.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide domain and hosting?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No, we don't provide domain and hosting services directly. However, we can recommend reliable and cost-effective domain and hosting providers based on your needs. Feel free to reach out to us for guidance on selecting the best options for your website.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you offer Website SEO as well?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, On-Page SEO is included in our premium package. It's highly recommended if it fits your budget. Contact us for more details.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What advantages does the premium package offer?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: We strongly recommend our Premium package, which includes five key features: On-Page SEO, SSL, one month of support, security, and backup. It also provides complete eCommerce functionality, expert guidance, and one-on-one consultation to help you manage and update your website with confidence.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you have a portfolio showcasing your recent WordPress Website or Landing Page work?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, we have a portfolio of recent WordPress Website and Landing Page projects. Contact us if you’d like to view examples of our latest work. We'd love to show.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can we communicate via email, Skype, or other methods for easier contact?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Sorry, but this goes against Fiverr's Terms of Service. All communication and payments must be handled through Fiverr's platform.
